{
  "texts": [
    "In future endeavors, we aim to assess the performance of QA models on more recent notes as part of ongoing research.",
    "To avoid data leakage, we use patients and their notes that did not appear in the gold-standard dataset generated by using notes from January 2022.",
    "We use the method described in Section Gold-standard dataset generation for building the test datasets using these notes.",
    "Similar to the gold-standard dataset, we manually review these test datasets in collaboration with a subject-matter expert.",
    "For the rest of the paper, we use the terms Cohort-Short and Cohort-Long to represent temporally out-ofdistribution notes in February and November, respectively."
  ]
}